<div class="markdown-heading" dir="auto"><h2 tabindex="-1" class="heading-element" dir="auto">Quick start</h2><a id="user-content-quick-start" class="anchor" aria-label="Permalink: Quick start" href="#quick-start"><svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"></path></svg></a></div>
<p dir="auto">Several quick start options are available:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><a href="https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap/archive/v5.3.8.zip">Download the latest release</a></li>
<li>Clone the repo: <code>git clone https://github.com/twbs/bootstrap.git</code></li>
<li>Install with <a href="https://www.npmjs.com/" rel="nofollow">npm</a>: <code>npm install bootstrap@v5.3.8</code></li>
<li>Install with <a href="https://yarnpkg.com/" rel="nofollow">yarn</a>: <code>yarn add bootstrap@v5.3.8</code></li>
<li>Install with <a href="https://bun.sh/" rel="nofollow">Bun</a>: <code>bun add bootstrap@v5.3.8</code></li>
<li>Install with <a href="https://getcomposer.org/" rel="nofollow">Composer</a>: <code>composer require twbs/bootstrap:5.3.8</code></li>
<li>Install with <a href="https://www.nuget.org/" rel="nofollow">NuGet</a>: CSS: <code>Install-Package bootstrap</code> Sass: <code>Install-Package bootstrap.sass</code></li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">Read the <a href="https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/getting-started/introduction/" rel="nofollow">Getting started page</a> for information on the framework contents, templates, examples, and more.</p>
